Vital Point to Capture?(28)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to play\b0 .
\par Black has an eye in the corner and it seems he has an eye on the left side as well.
\par
\par However if White plays a good sequence he can capture Black.
\par
\par This problem shows the power of the shortage of liberties.
\par
\par
\par }
