Dia. 01 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White's hane at 1 is a \cf1\b good move \cf0\b0 which \cf1\b prepares the shortage of liberties\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par Black has to answer with 2 and then White captures Black with the throw-in at 3.
\par
\par
\par
\par }
