Dia. 02 Pae?
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White throws-in with 1 and after Black takes with 2, Black can play the dansu at 3.
\par If it is played like this, Black resists with 4 and it becomes pae.
\par
\par However this \cf1\b sequence is terrible\cf0\b0 . Black is not going to capture with 2 but lives with 3.
\par
\par
\par
\par
\par }
