Dia. 03 Give up
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White's dansu at 1 \cf1\b gives up\cf0\b0  about capturing Black.
\par Black can easily live with the connection at 2.
\par
\par If White can't see how to capture, there is a big chance that Black will live like this.
\par The sequence in \b Dia. 01\b0  was excellent.
\par
\par }
